  "name": "RPlog_Caspar_Welcomes_Us",
  "title": "An Uneasy Welcome on Caspar",
  "summary": "The Sith Lord Malign and his Sarian pilot Axel Vichten wait under Marine guard at a Caspar starport, seeking an audience with the CDU government, while a clueless vending droid, HM743, hovers nearby taking lunch orders. Marine Captain Webb relays an initial flat refusal, prompting Malign to deliver a cold warning against trusting the Jedi and the Republic before turning to leave, with Vichten bitterly demanding the return of his confiscated ship and homeworld. The shuttle is recalled in mid-departure, and through Webb's helmet the Interim Presav Thomas Mahon himself opens a wary, world-weary negotiation with Malign, trading history and veiled threats. When Vichten's outbursts grow intolerable, Malign drains him unconscious with the dark side, then hands Mahon a datacard of intelligence as a gesture of trust before departing, leaving the bemused Marines to ferry the slumbering Vichten home.",
